          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0340P0_19991209_WH_17'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-ian-mccartney' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0340P0_19991209_WH_17' title='Link to this speech by Mr Ian McCartney' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
